name: Party Printables
description:
Birthday Party Printables

Please contact us before purchase so we can let you know what is included in your party printable pack**.

Most party printable packs usually consist of:
- cupcake wrappers
- cup or drink bottle wrappers (personalized with up to 24 names)
- menu or place cards (tent cards - personalized with up to 12 items)
- coordinating papers
- party circles
- bag toppers
- Happy Birthday Bunting


** some printable packs contain different items so please contact us for more information on the theme you are interested in.


www.mdslp.com.au



[ o r d e r i n g ]

1. Please let us know the following information in the “Notes to Seller” section:
- theme of the printable collection you would like
- Menu items or names for tent cards - maximum 24 names/items
- Cup Wrappers or Bottle Wrappers & names of guests - maximum 25 names
- A4 or US letter size
- Your email address

2. You will receive a link to download your high resolution PDF printable files within three business days of placing your order (often sooner!).



[ p r i n t i n g ]

Print as many copies as you'd like. Print them at home or take to a print/copy centre. For best results, we recommend you print on either matte photo paper, or card suitable for colour printing.

Party circles fit a 2" round/circle punch - this makes cutting them out so much quicker and easier!

Our watermark will not appear in your finished file.



[ q u e s t i o n s ? ]

If you have any questions, or would like a custom design, please don’t hesitate to convo us.



[ t e r m s . o f . u s e ]

This file is for personal use only. Selling, file-sharing and commercial use of this file is not permitted. 




Please visit our website for party ideas, favours, tutorials and inspiration!

www.mdslp.com.au

name: Personalised Invitation
description:
Choose your invitation from one of the many invitations that we have on our website: www.mdslp.com.au

Customized and Personalised Printable Invitation - we add your text and you print your invitation!

Text can be fully customized to your requirements.


[ o r d e r i n g ]

1. Please let us know the following information in the “Notes to Seller” section:
- name of the invitation you would like to order (or the link to the invitation from our blog)
- size 4x6 or 5x7
- JPG* or PDF** (if PDF, A4 or US Letter)
- Wording (including: Date, Time, Address, & RSVP information)

2. A proof of your personalized invitation will be attached to an email to you within 24 hours of your payment being cleared. Let us know via email any changes you need or want made. Most invitation orders can usually be finalized within a 24 hour period.

3. You will receive a link to download your high resolution JPG or PDF invitation.


* JPG - suitable for printing at a photo lab
** PDF - suitable for home printing on card stock or at a copy center - 2 invitations per page



[ p r i n t i n g ]

Print as many copies as you'd like. Print them at home or take to a print/copy centre. For best results, we recommend you print on either matte photo paper, or card suitable for colour printing.

Our watermark will not appear in your finished file.



[ m a t c h i n g . p a r t y . p r i n t a b l e s ]

After cupcake wrappers to match the theme? Or perhaps some drink bottle wrappers?

Coordinating printables are available for purchase in our shop:



[ t h a n k . y o u . c a r d s ]

Would you like to send a matching personal thank you to your guests? We also have thank you cards to match your invitation!



[ q u e s t i o n s ? ]

If you have any questions, or would like a custom design, please don’t hesitate to contact us.
